{"tid":1331814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁美芬：示威者到台灣尋求庇護因害怕承擔法律責任","createTime":"2019-07-19T05:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T13:36:48.000Z","uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":365,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"39d35114f30fc5db7ba3c471ca9144beabec83d4","tid":1331814,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:31:41.000Z","msg":"有傳媒報道，多名香港反對修訂《逃犯條例》示威者，自7月1日衝擊立法會後到了台灣，希望尋求庇護。<br />\n<br />\n經民聯立法會議員梁美芬說，今次衝擊事件後，已預計到有部分人會去外國或台灣等地尋求庇護，特別是那些故意挑起群眾的人士，相信他們會害怕承擔法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬又認為，如果特區政府有證據，證明相關人士蓄意使用武力，即使這些人已到其他地區尋求庇護，政府亦可把他們，列為繼續被追捕的嫌疑犯。他期望示威人士，表達意見之餘，要對自己的行為承擔責任。"},{"pid":"87f623a3795c25ec09c22893a23d6a9facb0de75","tid":1331814,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:31:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469216-20190719.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469216-20190719.htm&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=598f9309\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469216-20190719.htm&h=f33d6f15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469216-20190719.htm</a>"},{"pid":"da6f26400b55ac7831ecc11ed395bf707da453d7","tid":1331814,"uid":131843,"like":169,"dislike":1,"score":168,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:33:02.000Z","msg":"鬼唔知阿媽係女人"},{"pid":"edbf9e30a2de40a825bba76374188aa4508d5433","tid":1331814,"uid":78039,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:34:11.000Z","msg":"thx for ur information"},{"pid":"270aeed8c0ef785b350f2191350706766d51f52e","tid":1331814,"uid":282149,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:35:46.000Z","msg":"食屎啦 老鼠芬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck